subject: How to announce all to features acceptance. The aceeptance process takes long.
msgSnippet: We are all developing new features and bug fixes in to JUnit. You had to already see that this is not short time to accept a new design. When I submit
messageBody:
We are all developing new features and bug fixes in to JUnit. You had to already see that this is not short time to accept a new design.

When I submit something, then only Kent and David are announced. I would expect that much more developers are announced as well, or even the entire group. This may speed up.

What are you suggesting to speed up the acceptance?
